Announcement













Tuesday 18 July, 2017


 


RNS Number : 3920L Baillie Gifford Shin Nippon PLC 18 July 2017  

Baillie Gifford Shin Nippon PLC
 
Legal Entity Identifier: X5XCIPCJQCSUF8H1FU83
 
 
The Company announces the allotment of 100,000 Ordinary Shares of 10p each fully paid on 18 July 2017 under its block listing facility.  Following the allotment there are 42,095,497 Ordinary Shares in issue.  These shares were issued for cash on 18 July 2017 at a price of 683.00p per share.
 
Baillie Gifford & Co Limited
Company Secretaries
18 July 2017
 
Regulated Information Classification: Acquisition or disposal of the issuer's own shares
 

This information is provided by RNSThe company news service from the London Stock Exchange   END  IOEBVLFFDDFEBBQ



