                        We make no initial charge on any of our investments.  
                        However, funds do incur dealing costs which they may pass on to you (at cost).
                        Often these are free because funds get big economies of scale and can net trades off against each other, but if they do apply they are typically between 0% and 2% as a one-off cost.
                    

                    The fund managers' charges apply on a fund-by-fund basis.  The total shown is based on the initial proportion invested in each fund.
                



 


Cheaper than buying direct?


                            It’s usually cheaper to buy from us than it is to buy direct from the fund managers.  Weird?!
                        
    
                            It's because we can buy the funds for you from the fund managers at wholesale prices 
                            which are often much lower than the retail prices they charge to the general public.  
                            Usually this more than offsets the charges we and Cofunds make.
                        







Everything online, safe and secure


                        With our easy to use online account you get everything in one place.  No more lost paperwork.  No more hassle.
                    



                                From your account you can do all the standard things you'd expect to be able to do like:
                            

View your balance and recent transactions
Pay money in, take money out, change direct debits and switch money between funds
Update your address, bank and other details

But, because you're with SmarterInvestment, you'll also find thing you might not expect like:

Up-to-date "good case" vs "bad case" projections of what your investment might be worth in future
The latest results of our daily SmarterCare review of you investment
All your documents in one, easy-to-find, place
Tools to help you if you want to change the target for your investment or change its level of risk/return


                                And our robust security measures mean you can be confident your money is safe and secure.
                            




                                Your account area (click to try a demo account, no registration required)
                            







Portfolio

                
                                                    This is a single fund and not a portfolio that has been diversified by our algorithms.
                                            

                        Unlike some companies we're very transparent about how we make our money.   
                        We do not accept any commission or other payment from fund managers so you can be confident that our comparison tables are completely objective.  
                    

                        We only work for you and get paid via a 1.24% per annum charge on your investments.  
                        That's why you'll never find any "best buys", "top 150's" or other things like that.
                        You can find out more about how the portfolios in our comparison tables are selected.
                    





 







